1) Band-plots.net
Input files required for plotting with dx

2) futils
Generate the plot files in different formats based on bs_projected.dat file.

3) kproj_plot.py
Python script to read bs_projected.dat and generate figure.

4) kpts_path.f90 and ksplit.f90
generate and separate the k-points to multiple, respectively.

5) run_futils
Bash script to quickly process bs_projected.dat file.
Note that the path to futils should be specified in the script.


